metadata.name: PEPEROIDS #01
metadata.description:
PEPEROIDS IS A POST-PHOTOGRAPHY COLLECTION THAT EXPLORES THE LIFE OF PEPE THE FROG THROUGH 69 POLAROIDS FROM THE 50S TO THE 90S CREATED WITH AN AI.

THE COLLECTION CAPTURES IMAGINED MOMENTS FROM THE LIFE OF PEPE THE FROG BEFORE IT BECAME THE LEGENDARY CHARACTER AND MEME CREATED BY MATT FURIE THAT THE INTERNET POPULARIZED.
